    "body": "### Problem\n\nThe diff preview logic breaks the edit and they are applied incorrectly after: https://github.com/ibhagwan/fzf-lua/issues/2701\n\n### Steps to reproduce using \"nvim --clean -u minimal_init.lua\"\n\nAll steps to reproduce with the test are in the issue attached.\n\nThe test in the fzf-lua repo: https://github.com/IlyasYOY/fzf-lua/blob/0135a480db8e13cb4edd2c2a74ff4c10774c453c/tests/codeaction_spec.lua\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nThe `vim.lsp.util.apply_text_edits` is safe to apply multiple times.\n\nMaybe we should write the note about it in the docs.\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.12.2\n\n### Language server name/version\n\ngopls\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nmacos tahoe\n\n### Log file\n\n_No response_",
