        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Related: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/34954\n\nThe reason is that `apply_text_edits` is not a pure function; it modifies the passed text edits in place by adding a hidden `_index` field. Consequently, the behavior of the second call to `apply_text_edits` becomes inconsistent with the first.",
